                        <interp inst="t18741123-54-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Strongly recommended to mercy by the Jury on account of his youth and 'good character.—<rs id="t18741123-54-punishment-48" type="punishmentDescription">
